<div class="content-wrapper h-full w-full flex justify-center items-center">
    <section
        class="h-5/6 w-5/6 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-black shadow-2xl shadow-yellow-950 rounded-lg">
        <img class="h-full aspect-auto " alt="" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1682686581854-5e71f58e7e3f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1470&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDF8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D">
        <!-- <img src="" alt="Image of singleTrail.name singleTrail" srcset="<%# have a list of 3 image sources here from db %>"> -->
        <div class="flex flex-col h-full ml-5 w-1/2 justify-evenly">
            <div class="flex flex-col h-2/5">
                <p class="singleTrailName text-2xl font-bold "><%= singleTrail.name %></p>
                <a href="/trails/owners/<%=singleTrail.owner%>" class="singleTrailOwner text-blue-800 hover:text-red-800 active:text-violet-800"><%= singleTrail.owner %></a>
                <div class="singleTrailRankAndPrice flex flex-row">
                    <p class="singleTrailRank"><%= singleTrail.rank %></p>
                    <p class="singleTrailPrice">$<%= singleTrail.price %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="singleTrailTagDiv flex flex-col ">
                    <p class="">Tags:</p>
                    <div class="singleTrailTags flex flex-wrap justify-evenly">
                        <% for (let tag of singleTrail.tags) { %>
                        <a class="text-blue-800 hover:text-red-800 active:text-violet-800"
                            href="/trails/tags/<%=tag%><%=  %>"><%= tag %></a>

                        <% } %>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="details">
                <h3 class="text-lg">Details:</h3>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. At odit a quas enim sit tempora voluptatem
                    repellat similique. Esse ad accusamus ratione iste? Cumque consequatur necessitatibus quam, earum
                    consequuntur ipsum.</p>
            </div>
            <button
                class="w-1/3 border-solid border border-opacity-20 border-stone-950 rounded shadow-sm p-1 text-black hover:bg-green-700">Visit</button>

        </div>

    </section>
</div>




